# coreprover-bridge

Rust bridge to CoreProver Solidity smart contracts.

## Overview

This crate provides:
- Auto-generated contract bindings (via `ethers::abigen`)
- High-level client APIs
- Event listeners
- Type mappings between Rust and Solidity

## Usage

```rust
use coreprover_bridge::EscrowClient;

let client = EscrowClient::new(rpc_url, contract_address)?;
let tx_hash = client.create_escrow(order_id, seller, profile).await?;
```
